可以同邊個講先上黎r水吹姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6228c404f77b9a4db66aa093af0cbc2d24369b","tid":159101,"uid":20231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時間係度同其他人一齊討論下<br />\n不如死返去搵男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到幾忙幾忙，唔想對住個mon<br />\n又上黎R水吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你講得啱 但有時諗到dse又大壓力 對住佢又大壓力 因為想陪佢多d但又唔知講咩好 日日都係對住d書 我都係唔知可以同邊個講先上黎r水吹姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當對住佢變做一種壓力，你應該諗下問題係邊啦<br />\n你講到佢咁鬼好，又無話要求你做咩，可能你只係內疚呢。你咪直接同佢講或者做d野補償你心底個內疚，總之有咩就坦白同佢講就最好，有咩唔掂傾到掂，都唔明上黎搵d三唔識七既人傾有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efe19bd79033c76f6cdbe291f80cea95a768114","tid":159101,"uid":67201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"吾你老母 負皮上頁"},{"pid":"aec2998ca468a8ee2babae9acdf68694d8a5f7a1","tid":159101,"uid":25457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時間係度同其他人一齊討論下<br />\n不如死返去搵男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到幾忙幾忙，唔想對住個mon<br />\n又上黎R水吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}